st is well-structured with clear assertions. The use of defense-in-depth (CLI rejection + Agent logic filtering) is a high-quality approach.\n\n## Issues Found\nNone.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid. The combination of T-035 and T-036 provides robust protection against unauthorized or unknown action execution.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-036 @20260515t214233z-verify.md"}}
